- **UI:** Light theme (#FFFFFF / #333333) with Montserrat/Roboto typography
- **Sections:** Navbar (fixed), Hero (full-screen), Portfolio (dynamic filtering), L'Agence (team & missions), Contact (footer with map)
- **Identity:** Focused on "Atelier des Verre & Acier", highlighting mastery of glass and steel structures
- **Responsive:** Mobile-first approach with breakpoints (sm, md, lg)
