## Development Guidelines
- **Code Style:** Functional components, React hooks, no class components
- **Imports:** Use named exports for components
- **Accessibility:** Semantic HTML, proper alt texts, keyboard navigation support
- **Performance:** Lazy loading for images, optimized 3D rendering, smooth scroll behavior
- **Browser Support:** Modern browsers (ES2020+)

## Goals
- Maintain high performance and smooth 60fps animations
- Ensure "Architectural & Brut" design: plenty of whitespace, fine typography
- Emphasize technical precision and constructive solidity
- Keep codebase clean, modular, and maintainable
- Ensure responsive design works seamlessly across all devices
